    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Range of deep reddish blue colors resembling the color of indigo colorant, which is a vat dye obtained from indigo plants or artificially created.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093853/Webster's Third New International Dictionary (2002)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指一特定範圍的深紅藍色色彩，色近於靛藍著色劑。靛藍著色劑為一種染缸式染料，可從槐藍屬植物提煉或是由人工製造而得。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Reeks diep roodachtige blauwe kleuren die lijken op de kleur van de kleurstof indigo, een verfstof die wordt gewonnen uit indigoplanten of kunstmatig wordt geproduceerd.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gama de cores azul avermelhadas profundas que lembram a cor do corante índigo, que é um corante de cuba obtido de plantas de índigo ou criado artificialmente.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
